column2: A string of the tunnel ID.
column3: An integer of the ID of the node that describes the location of the tunnel.
column4: A string describes the construction type as defined in HAZUS Earthquake Model Technical Manual (FEMA 2022). Values allowed are 'Bored', 'Cut', or 'unclassified'.
column5: (Optional) Additional items which may be included for custom tunnel definitions.
